Transforming Data

Notes:

# install.packages('gridExtra') 
library(gridExtra) 
# 3 histgram in one plot
p1 <- ggplot(aes(x=friend_count), data = pf) + geom_histogram()
p2 <- p1 + scale_x_log10() # scaling layer 
p3 <- p1 + scale_x_sqrt()

grid.arrange(p1, p2, p3, ncol=1)
